. 
. * --- Compute policy-based treatment intensity ---
. * Uses pre-LOMR average NFIP policies / population as proxy for the
. * fraction of a zip's housing stock in the flood zone.
. * Better than geographic area share: reflects actual property exposure.
. bysort zip: egen _pre_policies = mean(cond(event_time < 0 | ever_treated == 0
> , n_policies, .))
(120 missing values generated)

. gen policy_intensity = _pre_policies / population
(120 missing values generated)

. replace policy_intensity = 0 if missing(policy_intensity)
(120 real changes made)

. drop _pre_policies

. label var policy_intensity "NFIP Policy Penetration (pre-LOMR)"

. sum policy_intensity, detail

