. * --- Pooled interaction regression (full sample, intensity-weighted) ---
. * β_τ (ibin_*) = baseline intensity LOMR effect (non-disclosure states)
. * γ_τ (disc_*) = additional intensity effect in mandatory disclosure states
. * Disclosure implied effect = β_τ + γ_τ (recovered via lincom)
